<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A9B06006001">
<title>
General Notes
</title>
<ptxt>
Welding method and number of welding points are the same on both sides. This repair instruction shows procedure for left side.
</ptxt>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A9B06006002">
<title>
Removal
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Drill out welding spots and remove dash side front panel with cowl top side front panel.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A9B0018.jpg" width = "183.000mm" height = "180.352mm" ver = "04" gw = "474" gh = "495"/>
